dsiter.row

Interface IParserMutator


  • public interface IParserMutator
    Interface for classes that parse strings and insert them directly into Rows.

    You probably won't have to implement this interface yourself: it comes with default implementations for all the standard types (e.g. uses Integer.parseInt for ints, Boolean.parseBoolean for booleans, etc. The only reason to make a custom implementation is if you want to parse values in some other format.
